      <title>贝莱德对 GIP 的大力押注让 Fink 的公司成为当地焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/blackrock-s-big-bet-on-gip-puts-fink-s-firm-in-local-spotlight</link>
